snippet.title: Smart Home Solver
snippet.description:
Hi, my name is Reed and this is my channel Smart Home Solver. I help you find the best smart home tech: smart security cameras, lights, thermostats, locks, and more.

I have loved adding smart home devices around my house and want to show others how easy and simple it can be.

Subscribing shows your support and makes sure you never miss a video. For more reviews, check out our website linked below.

Pitches and product inquiries: reed [at] smarthomesolver.com

As an Amazon Associate I earn from qualifying purchases. Links in descriptions are affiliate links.
